```
tasklean/
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ cmd/                     # Entry points
‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ tasklean/            # Main CLI
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ internal/                # Private application code
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ api/                 # API handlers
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ config/              # Configuration
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ models/              # Data models
